hanging on the following handshake 
send 0x44 -> get 0x7f
send 0xff -> get 0x0
eventually hitting system error

0x00 - NOP
0x01 - Part info
0x02 - Power up
0x09 - Test data?
0x10 - ID func info
0x11 - Set property
0x12 - Get property
0x13 - GPIO pin config
0x14 - ADC reading
0x15 - FIFO info
0x19 - EZconfig check
0x20 - get int status
0x21 - get ph status
0x22 - get modem status
0x23 - get chip status
0x31 - start TX
0x32 - start RX
0x33 - request device state
0x34 - change state
0x44 - read buffer
0x50 - FRR(?) A read
0x51 - FRR(?) B read
0x53 - FRR(?) C read
0x57 - FRR(?) D read
0x66 - Write TX FIFO
0x77 - Read RX FIFO

